tags.name: jwt-login
tags.description:
`jwt-login`
`a simple element to check for and fetch JWTs`

Events:

  * `jwt-login-refresh-error` - 

  * `jwt-changed` - 

  * `jwt-logged-in` - 

  * `jwt-token` - 

Attributes:

  * `refresh-url` {`string`} - refreshUrl to get a new JSON web token

  * `redirect-url` {`string`} - where to redirect for a login token if we REALLY are logged out

  * `logout-url` {`string`} - logout url

  * `url` {`string`} - url to get the JWT

  * `auto` {`boolean`} - auto, useful for demos

  * `method` {`string`} - Request method

  * `body` - Optional body, useful when doing posts

  * `key` {`string`} - Key that contains the token in local storage

  * `jwt` {`string`} - JSON Web token to securely pass around

Properties:

  * `refreshUrl` {`string`} - refreshUrl to get a new JSON web token

  * `redirectUrl` {`string`} - where to redirect for a login token if we REALLY are logged out

  * `logoutUrl` {`string`} - logout url

  * `url` {`string`} - url to get the JWT

  * `auto` {`boolean`} - auto, useful for demos

  * `method` {`string`} - Request method

  * `body` - Optional body, useful when doing posts

  * `key` {`string`} - Key that contains the token in local storage

  * `jwt` {`string`} - JSON Web token to securely pass around
